{"tid":512433,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)DOCTOR-X","createTime":"2017-12-28T12:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T19:23:11.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0f036037627bcd3e8cf5265e089b2c4536191765","tid":512433,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:59:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=0nV6d5TKzK7hGRrvUqXeLQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=21592d2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=0nV6d5TKzK7hGRrvUqXeLQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=b76660b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=0nV6d5TKzK7hGRrvUqXeLQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=da5d7b2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-8GsGQqrkW70/V8TU_Nt-YqI/AAAAAAAAAQ0/BvDi4xbpNm44AZELoRRaXNDRvKQViC0QwCEw/s1600/%E3%80%90%E6%97%A5%E5%8A%87%E3%80%91Doctor-X%E2%80%A7%E6%B4%BE%E9%81%A3%E5%A5%B3%E9%86%AB_%EF%BC%831%EF%BD%9E2%E5%AD%A3%EF%BC%8F2012+%EF%BD%9E+2013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-8GsGQqrkW70%2FV8TU_Nt-YqI%2FAAAAAAAAAQ0%2FBvDi4xbpNm44AZELoRRaXNDRvKQViC0QwCEw%2Fs1600%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258A%2587%25E3%2580%2591Doctor-X%25E2%2580%25A7%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E9%2581%25A3%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%2586%25AB_%25EF%25BC%25831%25EF%25BD%259E2%25E5%25AD%25A3%25EF%25BC%258F2012%2B%25EF%25BD%259E%2B2013.jpg&h=dae7d052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本劇主要描寫主人翁「大門未知子」，是一位外型和一般醫生形象截然不同的神秘女子，因為日本特殊的醫院文化，衍生出派遣醫生這樣的工作形式，她從醫大畢業後就到惡劣環境行醫練出了一身精湛的開刀技術，但她的表現近乎不通人情，時間一到就立刻下班，她在醫院從不參與派系鬥爭，與大學醫院醫局人員間的糾葛，僅以她最擅長的開刀技術在這樣的體系下生存，成為醫院裡醫生的眼中釘<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=0nV6d5TKzK7hGRrvUqXeLQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c4886026\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=0nV6d5TKzK7hGRrvUqXeLQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=72b11a9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4d9138c05227f03ebf926844ade860d40a29ce","tid":512433,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ec69feaaebd3b57e53e5b1f01ff69f9d12f524","tid":512433,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd907a26d6a2760da8a82d3b2e3c865896925189",